  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the steps to put my car in Ola Cab services?",
  "response": "To put your car into Ola's cab services, you\u2019ll need to register as a driver-partner with Ola. While the specific process may vary slightly depending on your location and any updates to the platform, here are the general steps:\n\n1. **Check Eligibility Requirements:**\n   - Ensure you meet the basic requirements set by Ola, which typically include having a valid driver's license, vehicle registration, and insurance.\n   - Your car must also meet certain specifications such as model, condition, and often the age of the vehicle.\n\n2. **Register Online:**\n   - Visit the Ola website or download the Ola Operator app.\n   - Look for the section to become a driver-partner and fill out the registration form with your details.\n\n3. **Submit Documents:**\n   - Submit the necessary documents including:\n     - Your driver's license\n     - Vehicle registration certificate (RC)\n     - Vehicle insurance\n     - Proof of address\n     - PAN card (for tax purposes)\n     - Bank details for payment processing\n     - Car permit (specific city/country requirements might apply)\n   \n4. **Vehicle Inspection:**\n   - Schedule an appointment for a vehicle inspection at one of Ola\u2019s designated centers.\n   - Your vehicle will be checked to ensure it complies with Ola\u2019s standards and requirements.\n\n5. **Training & Onboarding:**\n   - Attend the required training sessions conducted by Ola. They will brief you on how to use the app, customer service standards, and other operational procedures.\n   - You may need to go through a brief onboarding process which might involve creating a driver profile and learning how to navigate the app effectively.\n\n6. **Install the Ola App:**\n   - Download the Ola Driver app on your smartphone.\n   - Use the login details provided to access the app and start receiving ride requests.\n\n7. **Start Driving:**\n   - Once your account is activated and all steps are completed, you can begin accepting rides and earning money as a driver-partner in Ola Cab services.\n\n8. **Maintain Standards:**\n   - Keep your vehicle in good condition and adhere to Ola's guidelines to ensure a high rating and continued eligibility.\n\nIf you encounter any issues or require further assistance during any of these steps, it is advisable to contact Ola\u2019s support team directly for guidance.",
